name: Jetfuelvision
tagline: They say data is jet fuel. We're the jet.
body:
### About
We are a SAAS company that provides state of the art data processing techniques for time series data by building on the shoulders of giants. We know your time is valuable, so our APIs are designed for low latency and high throughput. You can hit us with all you've got.

Currently, we are in a closed beta. 

For inquiries, please reach out to jetfuelvision@gmail.com
If you are a customer with an issue, please include "SUPPORT: " in the subject line.
